BORG: Full conversion cyborg, human mind in a war machine

The Borg (Full Conversion Cyborg) has replaced most of their biological
body with a powerful mechanical chassis. What remains is a human mind
encased in Mega-Damage armor with built-in weapons and superhuman
strength.

Borgs are among the toughest characters in the game. They cannot be
Juiced or take most bionic additions (no room), and they require
maintenance instead of food. Their advancement is slower than most OCCs
to reflect their inherent power.

STARTING PACKAGE
  Attribute requirements: PS 14, PE 12.
  Flags: [Full Conversion Borg] [Cybernetic]
  Equipment: Full conversion cyborg body (military or civilian
    chassis), two integrated ranged weapons, vibro-blade, and
    maintenance toolkit.

